    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRAW, PLAY, FLIP, EARN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vault of the Vanquished</strong> is a <strong>rogue-like </strong> where you have been sent to the <strong>afterlife</strong>, after you were killed by the kings orders. You have now been <strong>resurrected</strong> and now you can collect and unlock powerful cards, to vanquish as many enemies as possible and bring peace to your Kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is built on the idea of <strong>RNG</strong>, bringing you through countless items to collect, and enemies to Vanquish! Push to Vanquish enough enemies to fight the boss of each zone, cleansing them one by one, and bringing peace to the Kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/fb28b0a44fb187204004c0a9c1b67584.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/fb28b0a44fb187204004c0a9c1b67584.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/fb28b0a44fb187204004c0a9c1b67584.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY YOUR CARDS RIGHT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to strategize your hand just right... from having a run where you are stacking buffs to stacking flips. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a00dce202c1f969484ec1115f6781fef.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a00dce202c1f969484ec1115f6781fef.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a00dce202c1f969484ec1115f6781fef.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE FLIP SIDE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run you need to Vanquish 11 enemies before making it to the FINAL BOSS of that location. But as the run continues enemies get harder and harder, so make sure to prep yourself for it... one way might be the...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/9cd0c472814244e353fbf337f1c37e56.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/9cd0c472814244e353fbf337f1c37e56.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/9cd0c472814244e353fbf337f1c37e56.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARACTER UPGRADES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you play through the game you earn yellow Gems which you can use to purchase PERMANENT upgrades for your character for your future runs! But another way to boost your character might be using some Unlocks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/2b165945fdc7adeccb077d9e28742116.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/2b165945fdc7adeccb077d9e28742116.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/2b165945fdc7adeccb077d9e28742116.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE COLLECTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While playing through the game and as you flip coins and Vanquish enemies you will unlock items you can use for any future runs! But the way you actually find these items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/27caa27c378d52b579ddc0fb6a888b37.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/27caa27c378d52b579ddc0fb6a888b37.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/27caa27c378d52b579ddc0fb6a888b37.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOOTING!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find loot after you kill an enemy, this can be anywhere from Active Abilities, to Cards you can play during the game. One way you can progress other than loot is...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a9e9fd4babdafce5e60ecd863d2b4043.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a9e9fd4babdafce5e60ecd863d2b4043.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/a9e9fd4babdafce5e60ecd863d2b4043.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE LAND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features multiple locations featuring different bosses and enemies for you to Vanquish on your journey! From a boring old castle to a village run by Goblins. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/6a8692cc5dcbf55469cc5d90a7e820df.poster.avif?t=1771872395\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/6a8692cc5dcbf55469cc5d90a7e820df.webm?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241250/extras/6a8692cc5dcbf55469cc5d90a7e820df.mp4?t=1771872395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AND MUCH MORE!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for launch in March! Lots of content, and even more on the way once the game is out!</p>",
